Chill	SOURCEPAGE:p.	SCHOOL:Enfeebling|Elemental	DESCRIPTOR:Ice	CLASSES:Blue Mage=1	CASTTIME:1 standard action	RANGE:Personal	TARGETAREA:A weapon or natural weapon	DURATION:(CASTERLEVEL) rounds (D)	SAVEINFO:Fortitude partial	SPELLRES:Yes	DESC:Creature Learned From (BM only): Lich Shade	DESC:&nl;The caster emulates biting cold of a lich shade's claws. The caster can imbue his weapon or natural weapon to inflict an additional 1d6 points of ice damage on a hit, and any creature that takes this additional ice damage must make a Fortitude save or be staggered for 1 round by the numbing chill.
