Hell Slash	SOURCEPAGE:p.	SCHOOL:Enhancing|Dark	CLASSES:Blue Mage=2	CASTTIME:1 swift action	RANGE:Personal	TARGETAREA:Slashing Weapon touched	DURATION:(CASTERLEVEL) rounds or until discharged	SAVEINFO:None/Partial	SPELLRES:No	DESC:Creature Learned From (BM only): Elite Skeleton	DESC:&nl;The caster emulates the dark energy from an elite skeleton to imbue his weapon. The caster must have a slashing weapon to use this spell. The next time this weapon strikes a creature, it discharges the dark elemental energy. The spell deals an additional 1d6 points of shadow damage against the target of the attack. In addition, the target of this attack must make a Fortitude save or suffer 1d4 Strength loss. The weapon loses this property if its wielder drops it or otherwise loses contact with it.
