Magic Circle against Good	SOURCEPAGE:p.	SCHOOL:Enhancing|Dark	CLASSES:Dark Knight=3	CASTTIME:1 standard action	RANGE:Touch	TARGETAREA:10-ft.-radius emanation from touched creature	DURATION:10 minutes/level	SAVEINFO:Will negates (harmless)	SPELLRES:No; see text	DESC:All creatures within the area gain the effects of a protection from good spell, and good summoned creatures cannot enter the area either. Creatures in the area, or who later enter the area, receive only one attempt to suppress effects that are controlling them. If successful, such effects are suppressed as long as they remain in the area. Creatures that leave the area and come back are not protected. You must overcome a creature's Spell Resistance in order to keep it at bay (as in the third function of protection from good), but the deflection and resistance bonuses and the protection from mental control apply regardless of enemies' Spell Resistance. This spell is not cumulative with protection from good and vice versa.
