Precognition, Defensive	KEY:Precognition (Defensive)	SOURCEPAGE:p.707	SCHOOL:Chronomancy	CLASSES:Time Mage=1	CASTTIME:1 standard action	RANGE:Personal	TARGETAREA:You	DURATION:(CASTERLEVEL) minutes (D)	DESC:Your awareness extends a fraction of a second into the future, allowing you to better evade an opponent's blows. You gain a +1 insight bonus to AC and on all saving throws. If caught in a situation where your Dexterity bonus isn't applied to your Armor Class, this bonus to AC and saving throws does not apply.
