Ray of Exhaustion	SOURCEPAGE:p.	SCHOOL:Enfeebling|Dark	CLASSES:Necromancer=3	CASTTIME:1 standard action	RANGE:Close	TARGETAREA:Ray	DURATION:(CASTERLEVEL) minutes	SAVEINFO:Fortitude partial; see text	SPELLRES:Yes	DESC:A black ray projects from your pointing finger. You must succeed on a ranged touch attack with the ray to strike a target. The subject is immediately exhausted for the spell's duration. A successful Fortitude save means the creature is only fatigued. A character that is already fatigued instead becomes exhausted. This spell has no effect on a creature that is already exhausted. Unlike normal exhaustion or fatigue, the effect ends as soon as the spell's duration expires.
