Toilsome Chant	SOURCEPAGE:p.860	SCHOOL:Enhancing	CLASSES:Bard=1	TARGETAREA:One living creature	SAVEINFO:Will negates (harmless);	SPELLRES:Yes (harmless)	DESC:You can perform this song as part of the action to begin an inspire competence bardic performance. The benefit of inspire competence persists for as long as is necessary to complete the target's next skill check using the chosen skill, even if you cease your bardic performance.
